{"tid":1127441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【林榮基流亡】為勸棄保赴台李倩怡回港言論認錯 「呢2年睇唔到法庭公正」","createTime":"2019-04-27T06:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T10:24:40.000Z","uid":28534,"like":58,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c2d00c78ed98e2de6e627faf06835f69f6d1ba37","tid":1127441,"uid":28534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:22:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190427/59535995\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190427%2F59535995&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=aeb0991e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190427%2F59535995&h=26c2a310\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190427/59535995</a><br />\n<br />\n前銅鑼灣書店店長林榮基流亡台灣的消息流出後，有網民「翻炒」他過去訪問提及，會勸因旺角騷亂而被控暴動及襲警罪、棄保潛逃台灣的少女李倩怡回港。他昨日接受《蘋果》訪問時坦然認錯，稱自己只是一個普通人，對香港問題亦有看錯之時，以為李的控罪不會成立，才想勸她回港，「當然我要負責，我係睇錯咗，我相信法庭係公正，但呢兩年睇唔到，2個後生被控暴動判6、7年」。他說，唯一安慰是李來台後未受傷害，「依家睇返轉頭，佢係唔適宜返香港」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n計劃來到台灣打工作，他林榮基始終希望能開書店，希望引入研究政治、經濟及文代的書籍，舉辦講座，從根本探究中國問題，「你唔能夠只係鬧，要搵根本原因。林自認曾是一名「大中華膠」，但自八九六四後，已「脫膠」亦不再承認自己是中國人，探討中國問題亦是以研究人權角度出發。記者問他，來到台灣，是選擇做台灣人，放棄做香港人？他稱，可以選擇台灣人，亦可以是香港人，「身份其實唔係好重要，重要係有權選擇成為咩人」。"},{"pid":"da36383ee8580bc925f3d864c45634557905d0dc","tid":1127441,"uid":90820,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:27:21.000Z","msg":"自己都走埋就180度轉軚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5cc7f29745f14e49b05b495af8941c73f3d5f6","tid":1127441,"uid":50124,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:28:38.000Z","msg":"其實個訪問幾耐之前?"},{"pid":"7d9e7cd29a8d40c88b8885c7754719cd77ac1d92","tid":1127441,"uid":4783,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:29:36.000Z","msg":"肯認自己睇錯咪岩<br />\n事實係睇錯左，亦好彩個女仔無返香港<br />\n咦咦，係咁幫佢spin話林榮基無錯個班入黎講下?<br />\n如果林榮基覺得自己無錯做咩道歉?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚多人話咩香港坐同中國坐唔同，去香港坐幾碌都無問題架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n案底令人生更精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e34e096e9521f9636c2fbf5e252911b0e36526","tid":1127441,"uid":82640,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:30:12.000Z","msg":"大大聲認錯<br />\n可以放過你<br />\n<br />\n但唔該再大聲啲<br />\n仲好多人聽唔到"},{"pid":"b4453fbd2616c640e2e3baffc13da1457f375109","tid":1127441,"uid":2429,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:32:07.000Z","msg":"知錯能改，善莫大焉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7baf51f13bcfe524db5846ada356d3d2a31003e7","tid":1127441,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"c9e34e096e9521f9636c2fbf5e252911b0e36526","tid":1127441,"uid":82640,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:30:12.000Z","msg":"大大聲認錯<br />\n可以放過你<br />\n<br />\n但唔該再大聲啲<br />\n仲好多人聽唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:32:44.000Z","msg":"蘋果訪問信3成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好佢自己本人拍片upload上youtube立此存照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863daadea6cca0cfd66ece25a1d48ee6cc21f861","tid":1127441,"uid":18251,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"da36383ee8580bc925f3d864c45634557905d0dc","tid":1127441,"uid":90820,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:27:21.000Z","msg":"自己都走埋就180度轉軚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:35:08.000Z","msg":"當日佢重信香港有法治先話勸人返嚟，今日佢睇透左香港係無法治所以佢都出走。有咩問題？"},{"pid":"7d6856af59574fe6c5007c029bbcc14d9a0add42","tid":1127441,"uid":47492,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote